<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10609119>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Classic examples of the tiger cat species complex: (a) the savanna tiger-cat (Leopardus tigrinus); (b) the new species, the clouded tiger-cat (Leopardus pardinoides); and (c) the Atlantic Forest tiger-cat (Leopardus guttulus). Drawings by Ricardo Ribeiro; photographs: (a) authors, (b) Johannes Pfleiderer, (c) authors." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10609119/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

